   <narrative xml:lang="EN">One Less Plastic Bottle on Our Streets &amp; Waterways</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will sensitize at least 100 businesses and 300 homes on the effect of plastic litter on our streets and environment. It aims to reduce plastic bottle litter by at least 1,000,000 bottles in 2 months and direct it to the recycling and from there implement a more permanent model. It will train at least 30 less privilege on low cost art forms from plastics.</narrative>
